message.content: "It's my business, I'll tell you more. You're going to take over command of Pericles. Am I right?" "Who told you?" "Little bird. Other half?" John nodded. "On me." Bawley shook his head. "All paid for by His Lordship," he said. "Expense account. You're a married man with a couple of kids. Can't go wasting your substance on a complete stranger. Set 'em up, darling!"
